Clone the repo

Extract the ZIP to a known folder on your computer.
(You should see files like manifest.json, popup.html, popup.js, style.css, etc.)

Open Chromeâ€™s Extensions Page

In Chrome, navigate to "chrome://extensions/".

Toggle Developer mode on (top-right corner).

Load the Extension(top-left corner).

Click Load unpacked.

Select the folder where you extracted the extension files.

The VaultText icon should now appear in your Chrome toolbar.

voila!
